87 // Maximum
95 static inline float32_t hpm_dsp_max_f32(const float32_t *src, uint32_t size, uint32_t *index)
96 {
97 #if HPM_DSP_CORE == HPM_DSP_HW_NDS32
98 #ifdef __zcc__
99  f32_t res;
100  tpt_max_f32(&res, index, src, size);
101  return res;
102 #else
103  return riscv_dsp_max_f32(src, size, index);
104 #endif
105 #endif
106 }

1059 static inline void hpm_dsp_add_q31(q31_t *src1, q31_t *src2, q31_t *dst, uint32_t size)

5799 static inline void hpm_ffa_cfft_q15(q15_t *src, uint32_t m)
5800 {
5801  fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
5802  xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
5803  xfer.src = src;
5804  xfer.dst = src;
5805  xfer.is_ifft = false;
5806  xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
5807  xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
5808  ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
5809 }

5830 #if defined(HPM_IP_FEATURE_FFA_FP32) && HPM_IP_FEATURE_FFA_FP32
5831 static inline void hpm_ffa_cfft_f32(float *src, uint32_t m)
5832 {
5833  fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
5834  xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
5835  xfer.src = src;
5836  xfer.dst = src;
5837  xfer.is_ifft = false;
5838  xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_FP32;
5839  xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_FP32;
5840  ffa_enable_fp_bias(HPM_FFA);
5841  ffa_set_coef_max_index(HPM_FFA, 0);
5842  ffa_set_output_max_index(HPM_FFA, 20);
5843  ffa_set_input_max_index(HPM_FFA, 20 - m);
5844  ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
5845 }
5846 #endif
5855 static inline void hpm_ffa_cifft_q15(q15_t *src, uint32_t m)
5856 {
5857  fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
5858  xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
5859  xfer.src = src;
5860  xfer.dst = src;
5861  xfer.is_ifft = true;
5862  xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
5863  xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
5864  ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
5865 }

6600 
6601 #ifdef HPM_MATH_NN_TINYENGINE
6602 #ifdef HPM_EN_MATH_DSP_LIB
6603 
6604 #include "riscv_math_types.h"
6605 #include <string.h>
6606 #include "riscv_simd_convert.h"
6607 
6608 #define LEFT_SHIFT(_shift) (_shift > 0 ? _shift : 0)
6609 #define RIGHT_SHIFT(_shift) (_shift > 0 ? 0 : -_shift)
6610 #ifndef __zcc__
6611 #define Q31_MAX ((q31_t)(0x7FFFFFFFL))
6612 #define Q31_MIN ((q31_t)(0x80000000L))
6613 #endif
6614 
6615 static inline void write_q15x2_ia(
6616  q15_t **pQ15,
6617  q31_t value)
6618 {
6619  q31_t val = value;
6620  (*pQ15)[0] = (val & 0x0FFFF);
6621  (*pQ15)[1] = (val >> 16) & 0x0FFFF;
6622  *pQ15 += 2;
6623 }
6624 
6631 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE q31_t hpm_nn_read_q15x2_ia(const q15_t **in_q15)
6632 {
6633  q31_t val;
6634 
6635  val = *(q31_t *)(*in_q15);
6636  *in_q15 += 2;
6637 
6638  return val;
6639 }
6640 
6649 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE q31_t hpm_nn_sat_doubling_high_mult(const q31_t m1, const q31_t m2)
6650 {
6651  q31_t result = 0;
6652  q63_t mult = 1 << 30;
6653 
6654  if ((m1 < 0) ^ (m2 < 0)) {
6655  mult = 1 - mult;
6656  }
6657  mult = mult + (q63_t)m1 * m2;
6658  result = mult / (1UL << 31);
6659 
6660  if ((m1 == m2) && (m1 == (int32_t)Q31_MIN)) {
6661  result = Q31_MAX;
6662  }
6663  return result;
6664 }
6665 
6674 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE q31_t hpm_nn_divide_by_power_of_two(const q31_t dividend, const q31_t exponent)
6675 {
6676  q31_t result = 0;
6677 
6678  const q31_t remainder_mask = (1l << exponent) - 1;
6679  int32_t remainder = remainder_mask & dividend;
6680 
6681  result = dividend >> exponent;
6682  q31_t threshold = remainder_mask >> 1;
6683  if (result < 0) {
6684  threshold++;
6685  }
6686  if (remainder > threshold) {
6687  result++;
6688  }
6689 
6690  return result;
6691 }
6692 
6693 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE q31_t hpm_nn_requantize(const q31_t val, const q31_t multiplier, const q31_t shift)
6694 {
6695  return hpm_nn_divide_by_power_of_two(hpm_nn_sat_doubling_high_mult(val * (1 << LEFT_SHIFT(shift)), multiplier),
6696  RIGHT_SHIFT(shift));
6697 }
6698 
6704 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE q31_t hpm_nn_read_q7x4_ia(const q7_t **in_q7)
6705 {
6706  q31_t val;
6707 
6708  val = *(q31_t *)(*in_q7);
6709  *in_q7 += 4;
6710 
6711  return val;
6712 }
6713 
6718 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE const q7_t *read_and_pad_reordered(const q7_t *source, q31_t *out1, q31_t *out2)
6719 {
6720  q31_t inA = hpm_nn_read_q7x4_ia(&source);
6721 
6722  *out2 = __SXTB16_ROR(inA, 8);
6723  *out1 = __SXTB16(inA);
6724 
6725  return source;
6726 }
6727 
6732 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE const q7_t *read_and_pad(const q7_t *source, q31_t *out1, q31_t *out2)
6733 {
6734  q31_t inA = hpm_nn_read_q7x4_ia(&source);
6735  q31_t inAbuf1 = __SXTB16_ROR(inA, 8);
6736  q31_t inAbuf2 = __SXTB16(inA);
6737 
6738  *out2 = __PKHTB(inAbuf1, inAbuf2, 16);
6739  *out1 = __PKHBT(inAbuf2, inAbuf1, 16);
6740 
6741  return source;
6742 }
6743 
6749 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE int32_t hpm_nn_read_s8x4_ia(const int8_t **in_s8)
6750 {
6751  int32_t val;
6752 
6753  val = *(int32_t *)(*in_s8);
6754  *in_s8 += 4;
6755 
6756  return val;
6757 }
6758 
6759 __STATIC_FORCEINLINE void hpm_nn_q7_to_q15_with_offset(const int8_t *src, int16_t *dst, int32_t block_size, int16_t offset)
6760 {
6761  int32_t block_cnt;
6762 
6763  /* Run the below code for cores that support SIMD instructions */
6764  int32_t in_q7x4;
6765  int32_t in_q15x2_1;
6766  int32_t in_q15x2_2;
6767  int32_t out_q15x2_1;
6768  int32_t out_q15x2_2;
6769 
6770  /*loop unrolling */
6771  block_cnt = block_size >> 2;
6772 
6773  /* First part of the processing with loop unrolling. Compute 4 outputs at a time. */
6774  const int32_t offset_q15x2 = __PKHBT(offset, offset, 16);
6775  while (block_cnt > 0) {
6776  /* convert from s8 to s16 and then store the results in the destination buffer */
6777  in_q7x4 = hpm_nn_read_s8x4_ia(&src);
6778 
6779  /* Extract and sign extend each of the four s8 values to s16 */
6780  in_q15x2_1 = __SXTAB16(offset_q15x2, __ROR(in_q7x4, 8));
6781  in_q15x2_2 = __SXTAB16(offset_q15x2, in_q7x4);
6782 
6783  out_q15x2_2 = __PKHTB(in_q15x2_1, in_q15x2_2, 16);
6784  out_q15x2_1 = __PKHBT(in_q15x2_2, in_q15x2_1, 16);
6785 
6786  write_q15x2_ia(&dst, out_q15x2_1);
6787  write_q15x2_ia(&dst, out_q15x2_2);
6788 
6789  block_cnt--;
6790  }
6791  /* Handle left over samples */
6792  block_cnt = block_size % 0x4;
6793 
6794  while (block_cnt > 0) {
6795  *dst++ = (int16_t)*src++ + offset;
6796 
6797  /* Decrement the loop counter */
6798  block_cnt--;
6799  }
6800 }
6801 
6802 #endif
6803 #endif
6804
